# Claude Agent

Specialization for Claude Code. Extends CLIAgent through composition. Sets command to `claude`, adds `-p` and `--output-format text` flags, translates Tools into `--allowedTools`, ModelID into `--model`.

Constructor: `NewClaudeAgent(profile: AgentProfile) -> ClaudeAgent`
